    {
      "id": "stage-03",
      "order": 3,
      "title": "Práctica guiada",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Pr&aacute;ctica guiada &mdash; Operaciones combinadas</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css\">\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js\"></script>\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js\"></script>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .tip { background: #f0fbff; border-left: 4px solid #6ac8ff; padding: 10px 12px; margin: 14px 0; }\n    .step { margin:.3rem 0; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Pr&aacute;ctica guiada</h1>\n  <p><span class=\"badge\">5.&ordm; grado</span><span class=\"badge\">Ejercicios</span></p>\n\n  <h2>Parte A: Propiedades</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 1 &mdash; Propiedad conmutativa</h4>\n    <p>Completa usando la propiedad conmutativa:</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) $250 + 430 = $ ___ $+ 250$</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) $1\\,800 + 3\\,200 = 3\\,200 +$ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) &iquest;Se puede aplicar la propiedad conmutativa a $15 - 9$? Explica.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 2 &mdash; Propiedad asociativa</h4>\n    <p>Resuelve agrupando de la forma que te resulte m&aacute;s f&aacute;cil:</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) $600 + 400 + 2\\,500 = $ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) $1\\,350 + 650 + 4\\,000 = $ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) $75 + 125 + 300 + 500 = $ ___</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Parte B: Estimaci&oacute;n</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 3 &mdash; Estimar resultados</h4>\n    <p>Redondea a la unidad de mil m&aacute;s cercana y estima:</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) $7\\,820 + 4\\,190 \\approx$ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) $56\\,300 - 23\\,700 \\approx$ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) $134\\,500 + 65\\,800 \\approx$ ___</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Parte C: Operaciones combinadas</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 4 &mdash; Resuelve paso a paso</h4>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) $(8 + 12) - 5 = $ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) $30 - (7 + 13) = $ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) $(45 - 20) + (10 + 5) = $ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">d) $100 - (25 + 30) + 15 = $ ___</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 5 &mdash; Con n&uacute;meros grandes</h4>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) $(15\\,000 + 5\\,000) - 8\\,200 = $ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) $50\\,000 - (12\\,000 + 18\\,000) = $ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) $(42\\,500 - 12\\,500) + (7\\,300 + 2\\,700) = $ ___</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 6 &mdash; Coloca los par&eacute;ntesis</h4>\n    <p>A&ntilde;ade par&eacute;ntesis para que la igualdad sea correcta:</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) $20 + 5 - 10 = 15$  &rarr; &iquest;D&oacute;nde van los par&eacute;ntesis?</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) $30 - 10 + 5 = 15$  &rarr; &iquest;D&oacute;nde van los par&eacute;ntesis?</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) $50 - 20 - 10 = 40$ &rarr; &iquest;D&oacute;nde van los par&eacute;ntesis?</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Parte D: Problemas</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 7</h4>\n    <p>Sof&iacute;a ten&iacute;a $\\text{Bs }150$. Recibi&oacute; $\\text{Bs }80$ de regalo y luego gast&oacute; $\\text{Bs }95$ en &uacute;tiles escolares. &iquest;Cu&aacute;nto dinero le queda?</p>\n    <p>Escribe la operaci&oacute;n combinada y resu&eacute;lvela.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 8</h4>\n    <p>En una biblioteca hay $12\\,500$ libros. Llegaron $3\\,200$ libros nuevos y se prestaron $1\\,850$. &iquest;Cu&aacute;ntos libros hay ahora?</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"note\">\n    <strong>Respuestas:</strong><br/>\n    1a) 430 &middot; 1b) 1&thinsp;800 &middot; 1c) No, la resta no es conmutativa<br/>\n    2a) 3&thinsp;500 &middot; 2b) 6&thinsp;000 &middot; 2c) 1&thinsp;000<br/>\n    3a) 8&thinsp;000 + 4&thinsp;000 = 12&thinsp;000 &middot; 3b) 56&thinsp;000 &minus; 24&thinsp;000 = 32&thinsp;000 &middot; 3c) 135&thinsp;000 + 66&thinsp;000 = 201&thinsp;000<br/>\n    4a) 15 &middot; 4b) 10 &middot; 4c) 40 &middot; 4d) 60<br/>\n    5a) 11&thinsp;800 &middot; 5b) 20&thinsp;000 &middot; 5c) 40&thinsp;000<br/>\n    6a) $(20 + 5) - 10 = 15$ &middot; 6b) $30 - (10 + 5) = 15$ &middot; 6c) $50 - (20 - 10) = 40$<br/>\n    7) $150 + 80 - 95 = 135$ Bs &middot; 8) $12\\,500 + 3\\,200 - 1\\,850 = 13\\,850$ libros\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n  document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n    renderMathInElement(document.body, {\n      delimiters: [{left: \"$$\", right: \"$$\", display: true},{left: \"$\", right: \"$\", display: false}]\n    });\n  });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
